data.description: Spacious 2-story, 3 bedroom home with new floor, freshly painted walls and ceilings. Enter into the large front living room that leads to a separate family room. This home also comes with a solar PPA that produces an estimated 14,000 kWh per year saving money on your energy bills. This gem is awaiting its new owner, so please come and show. *Sellers are very motivated.
